title: Dekton Spring Clamp 8 PC 2" Set - 32mm Jaw Opening, Compact Design with Strong Gripping Power, Durable Zinc-Plated Spring Clamps, Rubber Coating for Non-Slip Grip, Ideal for DIY and Professional Use.
features: DURABLE spring clamp set, zinc coated ANTI-SLIP rubber grip for comfort and ease of use JAW opening of 22mm with rubber tips to avoid damage to material being clamped IDEAL FOR carpentry, mechanics, crafts, DIY and more
description: The Dekton Spring Clamp Set is the perfect tool for securing materials during various projects, boasting a 32mm jaw opening that provides exceptional gripping power. Designed with durability in mind, these clamps are constructed from high-quality zinc-plated materials, ensuring they withstand heavy use without compromising performance. The rubber-coated grips enhance control and prevent slipping, making them ideal for woodworking, crafting, and home improvement tasks. With their compact size, these clamps are easy to maneuver and store, providing versatility for both DIY enthusiasts and professional tradespeople. The user-friendly spring-loaded mechanism allows for quick and effortless operation—simply squeeze to open, position your materials, and release to secure. Whether you're holding pieces together while glue dries or stabilizing materials during cutting, these spring clamps deliver reliable performance. Enhance your toolkit with the Dekton Spring Clamp Set and experience the convenience and efficiency it brings to your projects.
